{"word":"G2014 - ἐπιφαίνω - epiphaínō - ep-ee-fah'-ee-no - Appear","slug":"G2014","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιφαίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>epiphaínō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ep-ee-fah'-ee-no"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Appear"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03B9;&#x03C6;&#x03B1;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9; - epiphaino&#x0304;</b> - <i>ep-ee-fah'ee-no</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G5316\">G5316</a>; to <i>shine upon</i>, that is, <i>become</i> (literally) <i>visible</i> or (figuratively) <i>known:</i> - appear, give light."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1718\">G1718</a>, <a href=\"#/G2015\">G2015</a>, <a href=\"#/G2016\">G2016</a>, <a href=\"#/G5316\">G5316</a>, <a href=\"#/G5318\">G5318</a>, <a href=\"#/G5319\">G5319</a>, <a href=\"#/G5320\">G5320</a>, <a href=\"#/G5321\">G5321</a>, <a href=\"#/G5322\">G5322</a>, <a href=\"#/G5324\">G5324</a>, <a href=\"#/G5325\">G5325</a>, <a href=\"#/G5326\">G5326</a>"}]}